策略。这让你可以决定，你想反击他们正在做的事情，还是用你自己的策略进行攻击并迫使他们对你做出反应？” </p><figure id="attachment_3490932" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3490932" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3490932" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/glassbreakers-new-VR-game-from-developers-of-moss-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/glassbreakers-new-VR-game-from-developers-of-moss-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/glassbreakers-new-VR-game-from-developers-of-moss-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/glassbreakers-new-VR-game-from-developers-of-moss-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/glassbreakers-new-VR-game-from-developers-of-moss-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/glassbreakers-new-VR-game-from-developers-of-moss-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/glassbreakers-new-VR-game-from-developers-of-moss-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3490932" class="wp-caption-text"> 《玻璃破碎者：莫斯的冠军》图片来源：Polyarc</figcaption></figure><p>目前，该游戏已在 Meta Quest 2 上提供抢先体验。Polyarc 详细介绍了未来将其带到 Steam 和 PSVR2 等其他平台以及跨平台游戏的意图。</p><p>在其他新闻中，金属乐队 TesseracT 一直在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metal-band-tesseract-launch-vr-game-war-of-being-3482471">开发一款 VR 科幻游戏，该游戏与其专辑 War Of Being 相关</a>，作为“音乐和游戏之间的催眠桥梁”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/glassbreakers-is-the-new-multiplayer-vr-title-from-moss-developer-3490916">《Glassbreakers》是由《Moss》开发商开发的全新多人 VR 游戏，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
