phoenix-napoleon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/joaquin-phoenix-napoleon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">雷德利·斯科特</a>透露，他对即将上映的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/napoleon"><em>《拿破仑》</em></a>进行了“精彩”剪辑，该片时长近四个半小时。</p><p>他的下一部电影由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joaquin-phoenix">华金·菲尼克斯 (Joaquin Phoenix)</a>饰演法国领导人拿破仑·波拿巴 (Napoleon Bonaparte)，官方片长为 158 分钟。导演表示有一个加长版，他希望最终能看到曙光。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《帝国》</em></a>杂志 2023 年 9 月号（来自<a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/napoleon-ridley-scott-directors-cut-four-hours-1235706910/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> ）报道，这个近 270 分钟的版本“更多地讲述了约瑟芬在遇到拿破仑之前的生活。他希望苹果公司（资助这部电影的）最终能够放映这部电影。但他们现在所拥有的，绝不是微不足道的。 “这是一个令人震惊的故事，”菲尼克斯谈到拿破仑的一生时说道。 “希望我们能捕捉到一些最有趣的时刻。”</p><p>凡妮莎·柯比在影片中与菲尼克斯演对手戏，饰演拿破仑的妻子约瑟芬，该片计划于 2023 年 11 月 22 日在电影院上映。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="拿破仑 - 官方预告片（高清）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OAZWXUkrjPc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在接受<em>《帝国》</em>杂志采访时，柯比说道：“华金研究的是心灵，而拿破仑的心灵非常奇怪。电影就是这样的感觉。这有点奇怪，而且有一种强度。</p><p> “拿破仑并不像<em>《角斗士》</em>中的罗素·克劳那样坚忍和出色。他确实是一个独裁者，一个战犯。这不可能令人振奋，因为在我看来，那个人毫无必要地杀死了成百上千的人。为了什么？建立帝国，为了什么？最终，无论如何，这一切都瓦解了。这种疯狂的心理非常危险，而且非常奇怪。这就是它的写照。”</p><p>菲尼克斯此前曾与斯科特在 2000 年的电影<em>《角斗士》</em>中合作，他在片中饰演康茂德皇帝。谈起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joaquin-phoenix-didnt-know-what-to-do-before-napoleon-shoot-3475878">最近再次与导演合作</a>，菲尼克斯形容“非常怀旧”。</p><p> “The truth is, there was just a very nostalgic idea of working with Ridley again,” the actor said. “I had such an incredible experience working with Ridley on <em>Gladiator</em> , and I was so young. It was my first big production. I really yearned for that experience again, or something similar.”</p><p> He added: “He&#39;s approached me about other things in the past, but nothing that felt like it would be as demanding for both of us. And so I really liked the idea of jumping into something with Ridley that was going to be that.”</p><p> A sequel to <em>Gladiator</em> is currently in development with Paul Mescal as Lucius, the son of Maximus (previously played by Russell Crowe). <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/pedro-pascal-is-set-to-star-in-ridley-scotts-gladiator-sequel-film-3438298">Pedro Pascal was recently reported to have joined the cast</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ridley-scott-has-fantastic-four-half-hour-cut-napoleon-3490918">Ridley Scott has a “fantastic” four-and-a-half hour cut of &#39;Napoleon&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
